You can set different values to `displayedColumns` depending on user agent. Something like:

``` lang-ts
ngOnInit() {
  if (isMobileBrowser) this.displayedColumns = [&#39;mobile&#39;, &#39;column&#39;, &#39;set&#39;];
  else this.displayedColumns = [&#39;desktop&#39;, &#39;column&#39;, &#39;big&#39;, &#39;set&#39;];
```

